{"type": "article", "id": 29376, "title": "灵感来源于海胆的柜子", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-10T23:02:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160710214656fNU2Qd6CjM4yBTa0.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>仿生设计并不是什么新鲜的概念了，不过今天介绍的木制橱柜 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/40477735/Urchin\">Urchin</a> 着实让人觉得有点稀奇：乌克兰设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/Dimas1c\">Dmitry Kozinenko</a> 以海胆作为灵感来源，为橱柜的上下两端设计了看上去有些杂乱无章的木管，像是海胆外壳的刺。下方的木管起到了支撑的作用，上方的木管可以用来作为书挡，还可以用来插入其他物品作为装饰。Urchin 目前还处于概念阶段，尚未投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160710214710nUBATVRGDSw4gQoy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160710214710Wdo2Z9VI4NBaMJXn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160710214711j6JuExnsRyegkNLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160710214711FtLIzNpuRTQ36l1q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}